data.description: Beautiful home on the west side of Bakersfield. Home offers great open floor plan, kitchen was remodel back in 2020 Master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with walk-in shower, double closets. New floors in kitchen, living room and hallway, A/C replaced August 2020, roof only 5   years old. Extra large back yard with patio and sparkling pool for them hot summer days.
